ZH:唇亡齿寒是一个古老的谚语。
EN:"When lips are gone, teeth will be cold" is an old saying.
ZH:唇亡齿寒表示一个团队中，每个成员都相互依赖。
EN:"唇亡齿寒" implies that in a team, each member relies on each other.
