EN:"唇亡齿寒" can be applied to various collaborative relationships.
ZH:唇亡齿寒也体现了互助的概念。
EN:"唇亡齿寒" also embodies the concept of mutual assistance.
ZH:唇亡齿寒是指相互之间必须互相支持。
EN:"唇亡齿寒" means that mutual support is necessary between each other.
ZH:只有团队内部紧密合作，才能避免唇亡齿寒的情况。
EN:Only by close cooperation within the team can we avoid the situation of "When lips are gone, teeth will be cold".
